Views
 - V: hierarchy view
 - i: toggle display of idle tasks
 - f: add or remove a field
 - x: set in bold the sorted column
 - b: backlight on the sorted columns(only if the sorted columns is in bold (X))
 - 1 display all CPUs

Sorting
 - M: sort by memory
 - P: sort by CPU usage
 - T: sorty by time
 - R: reverse sorting

